snippet.title: Vortex iPod Nano Gameplay
snippet.description:
In this video, I am playing several levels of the game Vortex on my old iPod Nano.

Smash Hit - Level 11 (Let's Play): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3dxUbp45ygU

Subscribe to see more gameplays: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=cgameworld

Did you know? - Vortex was first introduced in January 2007 and it has been included in all iPod nano and classic models since. 
The final iPod that shipped with this game was discontinued in 2014.

This game is pretty nostalgic to me. I used to play it all the time back in 2008/09.

Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/Cgameworld
